title: De Dag (The Day) - season 1 (HC Eng subs)
description: De Dag (The Day) - season 1 The nerve-racking events of a cold winter's day, seen from two different perspectives. The odd episodes tell the story of a team of police negotiators and special forces who respond to a hostage crisis in a small bank branch. The even episodes tell exactly the same events, only through the eyes of the criminals inside and their victims. Not my rip, reencoded to a smaller size: 1280 x 720p, MKV, H.264, WEB-DL Aired 2018 12 x 40 - 58 minute episodes Screenshots: https://i.imgur.com/DWzMZla.jpg https://i.imgur.com/a2IYkQx.jpg https://i.imgur.com/rbnRVOb.jpg Please seed and share with others. :)
